
Make it pretty? Bare bones html doesn't distract, or inspire.

Validation. The blog model doesn't require name or desc. It also doesn't enforce uniqueness.
I'm not sure what happens to the controller code, when the model becomes pickier.

Posts -- 0..* per blog; each post has a headline/title and body/content. The title and body should
both support reStructuredText and Pygments. I also want to keep a revision history.

SEO friendly URLs -- search by name. 
